(192, 'elementor_remote_info_feed_data', 'a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:46:\"NFT 101: A Beginner’s Guide for Web Creators\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:298:\"NFTs have taken the world by storm, providing web designers with fresh opportunities to earn money and distribute their work to larger audiences around the globe. In this article, we\'ll break down what NFTs are and how to use them practically (plus, a sneak peek at our new NFT landing page kits!).\";s:7:\"created\";i:1651578283;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:114:\"https://elementor.com/blog/nft-web-design/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:1;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"What Is Inclusive Web Design?\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:297:\"When designing a website, it is important to keep in mind that not all users interact with it in the same way. Using inclusive design will help you remove bias and assumptions from your website and ensure that users will not feel excluded. Keep reading to learn how to master this modern approach.\";s:7:\"created\";i:1651142542;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:120:\"https://elementor.com/blog/inclusive-web-design/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:2;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"How To Grow Your Business Using Elementor Cloud Website\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:313:\"In our ‘Community Talks’ event, four leading web creators held a panel discussion with practical tips on how you can incorporate Elementor Cloud Website into your business model to earn more. Uncover low-hanging fruit opportunities and learn to hunt down new avenues for business with Elementor Cloud Website.\";s:7:\"created\";i:1651067671;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:155:\"https://elementor.com/blog/how-to-grow-your-business-using-elementor-cloud-website/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:3;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:59:\"Word-of-Mouth Marketing: How To Build a Successful Strategy\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:337:\"One of 