t online reservation system. Sailing brings to you a perfect idea for your business if you want to launch a Hotel Booking Website. The integration of   WP Hotel Booking Plugin   gives you everything you need to manage your booking system easily. \n\n\nAmazing Hotel WordPress Theme\n\nComplete Hotel Booking System  +  Room Management  +  Coupon Management  +  Pricing Plans Management  +  Extra Packages Management  +  Block Special Date Management  +  Reports  +  Compatible with WPML  +  4 Payment Gateways (Offline Payment, Authorize.net, PayPal, Stripe)  +  WooCommerce Integrated  +  and more…\n\n	 What else \";s:16:\"description_html\";s:9166:\"<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/log/sailing-hotel-wordpress-theme-changelog/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-changelog.jpg\" alt=\"Sailing | Hotel WordPress Theme - 1\" /></a> </td>\n<td><a href=\"https://docspress.thimpress.com/sailing/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-docs.jpg\" alt=\"Sailing | Hotel WordPress Theme - 2\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/how-to-get-help-from-the-thimpress-support/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-support.jpg\" alt=\"Sailing | Hotel WordPress Theme - 3\" /></a></td>\n</tr> \n</table>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://thimpress.com/wordpress-hotel-theme-sailing/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hotel WordPress Theme &#8211; Sailing</b></a>  is a WordPress theme for hotel, hostel, resort or any other accommodation services with an excellent online reservation system. Sailing brings to you a perfect idea for your business if you want to launch a Hotel Booking Website. The integration of <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-hotel-booking/\" rel=\"nofollow\">  WP Hotel Booking Plugin </a>  gives you everything you need to manage your booking system easily. \n</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"item-description__amazing-hotel-wordpress-theme\">Amazing Hotel WordPress Theme</h2>\n\n<p><b>Complete Hotel Booking System</b>  +  <b>Room Management</b>  +  <b>Coupon Management</b>  +  <b>Pricing Plans Management</b>  +  <b>Extra Packages Management</b>  +  <b>Block Special Date Management</b>  +  <b>Reports</b>  +  <b>Compatible with WPML</b>  +  <b>4 Payment Gateways (Offline Payment, Authorize.net, PayPal, Stripe)</b>  +  <b>WooCommerce Integrated</b>  +  <b>and more&#8230;</b>\n\n	</p><p> What else do you need for your amazing WordPress based hotel booking website? \n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/hotel-wordpress-theme-sailing-2.png\" alt=\"Hotel WordPress Theme\" /></p>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"item-description__complete-hotel-booking-with-wp-hotel-bookingplugin\"><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/hotel-wordpress-theme-sailing/13321455#item-description__amazing-hotel-wordpress-theme\"><b>Complete Hotel Booking with WP Hotel BookingPlugin</b></a></h3>\n<p> The online reservation system of our  <b>Sailing- Hotel WordPress Theme</b>  is managed by  <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-hotel-booking/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> WP Hotel booking </a>  &#8211; a great hotel management plugin by ThimPress itself. WP Hotel Booking Plugin is already used by more than 1000 hotels, resorts all over the world. From here, you will have full control over rooms, bookings, customers, coupons, room types, room capacities, pricing plans and settings. </p>\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tUkVTXDtd8g\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n  <img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Hotel-WordPress-theme-Hotel-Booking-Plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Hotel WordPress theme\" />\n</a>\n\n<p>» <strong>Booking multiple Hotel Rooms with Cart</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Pricing Plans</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Coupon Management</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Report System</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Room Extra Services</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Room Management</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Block Special Date</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Customers Management</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Search rooms</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>WooCommerce support, using WooCommerce to handle payment</strong></p>\n\n<p>» <strong>Payment Gateways</strong></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"item-description__5-hotel-demos-w-1-click-demo-importer\"><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/hotel-wordpress-theme-sailing/13321455#item-description__amazing-hotel-wordpress-theme\">5 Hotel Demos /w 1 Click Demo Importer</a></h3>\n<p>\nWordPress Hotel Theme &#8211; Sailing has a design with 8 home-pages for you to set up your website. The attractive &#8220;About us&#8221; and &#8220;Gallery&#8221; pages also &#8220;kill&#8221; any visitor from the first sight. With the availability of WooCommerce, WordPress Hotel Theme &#8211; Sailing can be any online shop where you can set up products, features, price, variation&#8230;. In order to make better marketing, Sailing provides social media features to share information and find potential customers via Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, blog, and newsletters. Besides that, this WordPress Hotel Theme also supports translation ready even with RTL languages, Mobile-friendly, full responsiveness, Retina ready and SEO optimized.\n</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"item-description__stunning-premium-slider-for-your-hotel\">Stunning Premium Slider for your Hotel Booking website&lt;</h3>\n<p>\n Sailing comes with Revolution Slider &#8211; a premium plugin to deliver your website with high customization, transitions, effects and custom animations. The drag and drop, responsive page builder &#8211; SiteOrigin is also included here to simplify building any post, page and content of your website. Furthermore, the Sailing &#8211; WordPress Hotel Theme supports other plugins such as Black Studio TinyMCE Widget to adds a new &#8220;Visual Editor&#8221; widget type based on the native WordPress TinyMCE editor, Testimonials By  <a href=\"https://thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> ThimPress </a>  &#8211; a plugin that allows you to show off your testimonials, WordPress Importer to import posts, pages, comments, custom fields, categories, tags and more from a WordPress export file etc. \n</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"item-description__ultimate-seo-optimized\"><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/hotel-wordpress-theme-sailing/13321455#item-description__amazing-hotel-wordpress-theme\">Ultimate SEO optimized</a></h3>\n<p> By using our Sailing Hotel WordPress Theme, you get your hotel website ranked significantly higher on search engines. Every title, heading, meta tags have been optimized carefully as the way Google loves it.  <a href=\"https://goo.gl/J2QmgH\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Structured Data </a>  is implemented deeply to make your site look fancy on Google search results. We coded for not only blog posts, but WooCommerce products, room too. </p>\n\n<h3 id=\"item-description__discover-more-about-wordpress-hotel-theme-sailing\">Hotel WordPress Theme &#8211; Sailing in a Glance&lt;</h3>\n<p> Sailing is a Creative WordPress theme suitable for travel, tour, hotel booking, room booking, housing, listing, or airbnb &#8211; bed and breakfast service. If you want to build a hotel website on WordPress, you can definitely count on Sailing as your WordPress theme as it provides the features of a listing, hotel and travel website that can save you tons of time and effort. </p>\n<ul>\n    <li>Excellent online hotel reservation managed by <b>WP Hotel Booking</b>  plugin. </li>\n    <li><strong>Revolution Slider.</strong></li>\n    <li><strong>Drag &#38; drop, responsive SiteOrigin page builder.</strong></li>\n    <li>Responsive &#38; Mobile-Friendly.</li>\n    <li>Retina ready.</li>\n    <li>SEO optimized.</li>\n    <li>Social media sharing.</li>\n\n    <li>WooCommerce ready.</li>\n    <li>Post formats &#8211; Standard, Gallery, and Video.</li>\n    <li>Built on latest Bootstrap 3 &#38; FontAwesome 2.</li>\n    <li>Styles has written by LESS CSS. </li>\n    <li>Live preview Customi